                        description "0x8864/PPPoE Session/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8864
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 933 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 966 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 999 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                        exit
                    exit
                    no shutdown
                exit
            exit
        exit
    exit

        network 500 create
            description "for marking"
            ingress
                default-action fc be profile in
                dscp be fc be profile in
                dscp cs1 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs2 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs3 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs4 fc h1 profile in
                dscp cs5 fc af profile in
                dscp nc1 fc nc profile in
                dscp nc2 fc af profile in
                lsp-exp 0 fc be profile in
                lsp-exp 1 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 2 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 3 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 4 fc h1 profile in
                lsp-exp 5 fc af profile in
                lsp-exp 6 fc nc profile in
                lsp-exp 7 fc af profile in
            exit
            egress
                remarking
                fc af
                    dscp-in-profile cs5
                    dscp-out-profile cs5
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 5
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 5
                exit
                fc h1
                    dscp-in-profile cs4
                    dscp-out-profile cs4
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 4
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 4
                exit
                fc nc
                    dscp-in-profile nc1
                    dscp-out-profile nc1
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 6
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 6
                exit
            exit
        exit
    exit

            next-hop-resolution

            group "ibgp"
                family vpn-ipv4
                type internal
                peer-as 64759
                local-address 61.130.159.18
                neighbor 61.130.159.16
                    shutdown
                    description "JH-JH-CZ-SR-SR12-1.MAN"
                exit
                neighbor 61.130.159.17
                    shutdown
                    description "JH-JH-CN-SR-SR12-1.MAN"
                exit

                exit

                exit
                neighbor 61.174.80.90
                    description "JH-JH-CZ-RR-C7304-1.MAN"
                exit
            exit
            group "pgCR"
                family ipv4
                keepalive 60
                hold-time 180
                type internal
                preference 200
                export "rpSET_COMM_OUT" 
                peer-as 64759
                local-address 61.130.159.18
                neighbor 61.130.158.4
                    description "to:JH-JH-CZ-CR-1.MAN.CRS"
                exit
                neighbor 61.130.158.8
                    description "to:JH-JH-CZ-CR-1.MAN.CRS"
                exit
            exit
            group "guard"
                family ipv4
                type external
                export "export-direct-to-guard" 
                peer-as 65501
                local-address 61.174.193.17
                neighbor 61.174.193.18
                    family ipv4
                exit
            exit
            group "ibgp "
            exit
            no shutdown
        exit

            exit
        exit
    exit
#--------------------------------------------------
echo "System Time NTP Configuration"
#--------------------------------------------------
    system
        time
            ntp
            exit
        exit
    exit

exit all

# Finished SAT OCT 14 17:00:58 2017 UTC
*A:JH-YW-BW-SR-1.MAN.7750#
